description:
Easter Whispers is a masterpiece woven from the imaginative threads of three extraordinary artists: @ronansavazy, @FujiiSol, and @peterbo_sol. Together, we have conjured magic.

This creation is inspired by the majestic Year of the Dragon, which symbolizes power, fortune, and transformation. In the spirit of Easter, it celebrates renewal, joy and the playful spirit of rabbits. And woven into its tapestry is the vibrant heartbeat of our Solana family, each character a hero who embodies the resilience and unity of our community.

Embark on a journey through realms where legends come to life, where each brushstroke whispers secrets of ancient wisdom and boundless imagination. Discover the magic of Easter Whispers and let it ignite your spirit with wonder and awe.

About the Artists

Peter:
Peter is a simple person who embraces simplicity and views the world with the curiosity and wonder of a child. His positive approach to life enables him to find valuable lessons in every experience, transforming them into opportunities for growth and continuous learning. His open-mindedness and ability to see the good in everything around him make a passionate creator, capable of capturing the essence of life in his artworks.

Vaz:
From unknown to virality, y00ts changed the game for Vaz. His early work caught OKB’s eye, but finding his true voice took time. Stepping back from Web3 in 2023, he honed his craft, leaving behind the "Boxibly" era.
Next came "Sticky Tapes," a collection that stuck (pun intended!). Degen Poet, Marculino, Timethief, even Cabanimation - all rocking those as PFPs. Boom! Viral fame erupted.
But the journey wasn't over. "Sticky Tapes" was a stepping stone, not the peak. Paperpeeps, the current lovechild, showcases Vaz’s transformation. Less than a year, and his style is unrecognizable from before.

Fujiisol:
Fujiisol is a pioneering pixel artist whose journey began in 2021 on Solana. Renowned for his endearing and vibrant pixel creations, Fujiisol specializes in anime-inspired artwork and captivating profile picture designs, captivating audiences with his unique style and creative flair.
